th-rate-chinese-study-finds?utm_source=rss_feed</guid><link/> https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3221097/screening-technology-can-boost-ivf-live-birth-rate-chinese-study-finds?utm_source=rss_feed<author><![CDATA[Echo Xie]]></author><category>消息</category><category>中国</category><category>科学</category><category>中国人口</category><category>药品</category><category>中国健康</category><category>生殖健康</category><category>筛查技术可提高试管婴儿活产率</category><category>中国研究发现</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[As US-China rivalry mounts, South Korea wants to be a ‘global pivotal state’ but it’s not as easy as it sounds]]></title><description><![CDATA[<p>韩国总统<a href="https://www.scmp.com/topics/yoon-suk-yeol?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3220960_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="ce52158a-9e8d-4c7c-9a6e-ef5cf83e5ce1" data-entity-type="taxonomy_term" data-entity-bundle="topics">尹锡烈</a>表现出色。上个月在白宫，美国总统<a href="https://www.scmp.com/topics/joe-biden?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3220960_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="37293521-5cf3-479b-91f0-ec101e38ef15" data-entity-type="taxonomy_term" data-entity-bundle="topics">乔·拜登</a>和尹恩惠表明他们两国步调一致，无论是在打击朝鲜核计划、协助乌克兰对俄罗斯开战，还是改善与东京的关系方面。</p><p>言归正传，Yoon 的目标是提升首尔作为“全球枢纽国家”在该地区的作用和贡献——韩国去年 11 月发布的“自由、和平与繁荣的印太地区战略”中强调了这一术语。他还提倡新的韩国-东盟团结倡议 (KASI)。 KASI 于 2022 年 11 月在东盟-韩国（韩国）峰会上首次宣布，寻求将东盟-韩国关系提升为全面战略伙伴关系。它还寻求通过一系列促进战略协调和全面安全合作的建议来提高韩国的地区地位。 </p><div class="meter__linear relative" id="default-meter-page-views-11"><img width="auto" height="1" src="https://www.scmp.com/images/1x1.png" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="dm__l3"><hr class="vertical-line"><div class="dm__lw"><svg class="dm__l" height="24" viewBox="0 0 18 24" width="18" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><g style="stroke:#000;fill:none;fill-rule:evenodd;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-width:1.5"><rect height="13.5" rx="1.5" width="16.5" x=".75" y="9.7